{"tid":759290,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"ps4 fifa pro club d1球會招隊友參加比賽","createTime":"2018-07-28T12:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T18:08:22.000Z","uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e55947fc7e47ae0c22fda8c9f72e4e195849778e","tid":759290,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"我地球會組軍幾個月後嘗試參加vpl s19<br />\n可惜人數不足 成績並不太理想<br />\n<br />\n球會簡介<br />\n。每晚大概2200-0100開波<br />\n。以4321/433為主要陣式<br />\n。以防反快速反擊為主<br />\n。所以需要大家現位走位<br />\n<br />\n現希望招到更多full time 隊友參加比賽：<br />\n。數名識打防中嘅前場球員（若有機會大家試下夾下嘅話 將會先試防中位置）<br />\n。數名後防 <br />\n。1名龍門<br />\n<br />\n隊友要求：<br />\n。Full time 隊友<br />\n。每星期出席4-5日 (part time暫不考慮）<br />\n。打機時會開mic交流 營造良好氣氛<br />\n。互相尊重對方<br />\n<br />\n麻煩有興趣同我地夾下嘅tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/Eyikea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FEyikea&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bei7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=480dca66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Eyikea</a>"},{"pid":"1a8ac328c7f0f4d3d55855f8ce466149b412c833","tid":759290,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ea64ce972ea0c9320018e31dc17854f940929d","tid":759290,"uid":136369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"你邊隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc4f8e7700905ca3c60d44ec2fd4835e6df7058","tid":759290,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:01:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9166bbe2664b131a7cbddba222d33f0cf7c0e5a1","tid":759290,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:19:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b5ab5fe62de2b1425f72566189f529f2d37f55"